OL,4,CBolsonaro: Brazil's president ordered
OL,5,Cto pay damages to journalist
OL,6, A Brazilian court has ordered President
OL,7, Jair Bolsonaro to pay compensation to a
OL,8, journalist after he made degrading
OL,9, comments about her.
OL,11,FMr Bolsonaro had suggested last year
OL,12,Fthat Patricia Campos Mello had offered
OL,13,Fsex to a source for negative
OL,14,Finformation about him.
OL,16,FThe judge said Mr Bolsonaro's remarks
OL,17,Fhad damaged the journalist's honour.
OL,19,FThe president was told to pay her
OL,20,F20,000 reais (#2,500; $3,500) in
OL,21,Fdamages. He can appeal the ruling.
